# Frontend Component Conventions

## Component Structure
- Use "use client" directive for client components
- Export named components
- Place primitive components in /src/components
- Follow Radix UI patterns for compound components

## Props Pattern
- Extend HTML element props
- Use VariantProps for styling variants
- Include asChild prop for slot composition
- Use React.ComponentProps for primitive extensions

## Styling
- Use class-variance-authority (cva) for variants
- Follow Tailwind CSS naming conventions
- Use data-slot attributes for component parts
- Use cn utility for class name merging

## Accessibility
- Include ARIA attributes
- Support keyboard navigation
- Handle disabled states
- Implement focus management